    "description": {
        "en-US": "<b>NOTE: QuickFilterToolbar has been superseded by <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/thunderbird/addon/totalquickfilter/\">TotalQuickFilter 2.0</a>.</b>\n\n<b>QuickFilterToolbar</b> turns the stock message filter elements into a full toolbar.  <ul>Features include:\n<li>Toolbar customization: All buttons and bars are fully moveable/removeable.  Any other button or item may be added to the Quick Filter Toolbar via the <b>Customize...</b> dialog.</li><li>Keyboard support: All buttons and elements contain tabstops, and toggling is performed by &lt;enter&gt;.  The tag bar uses ctrl-enter to negate a tag (like a right click currently).</li><li>Full width: the toolbar is usable with the Vertical layout (and Stacked, available in the <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/morelayouts\">MoreLayouts extension</a>).</li><li>Tweaks: several tweaks for better usability, such as updating the tags bar to match current filters; ensuring element layouts conserve space; ensuring elements integrate with well known xul look and feel conventions, which makes for easy theming.</li></ul>\n<b>Comments and Questions:</b> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://outgoing.prod.mozaws.net/v1/fca1635717c79763c9aa488dce7ee00a2c6ec615c25432fe3ee29cc19dc13de9/http%3A//forums.mozillazine.org/viewtopic.php%3Ff=48&amp;t=2626433\">QuickFilterToolbar forum thread</a>."
    },
